| **Error Message / Symptom**                                                                   | **Root Cause**                                                        | **Resolved?** | **Resolution**                                                                                                         |
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `DBusException: Failed to connect to socket ... system_bus_socket: No such file or directory` | Race condition: BlueZ not ready before dbus-python tried to connect.  | ✅ Yes         | Added retry logic using `wait_for_dbus_socket()` and ensured D-Bus was fully started before `SystemBus()` call.        |
| Some discovered devices raise `DBusException` when trying to fetch `Adapter`                  | Devices were not fully initialized or not part of current adapter.    | ✅ Yes         | Added a check to compare device adapter path with current adapter. Skipped those not matching or missing adapter info. |
| Clicking “PAIR” on some devices throws an error about adapter not found                       | UI table displayed invalid/incomplete devices (missing adapter path). | ✅ Yes         | Filtered out such devices in the table population loop using a `try/except` and adapter comparison.                    |
| Empty rows appearing in the discovery table (visual glitch)                                   | UI pre-allocated rows before filtering out invalid devices.           | ✅ Yes         | Switched from pre-setting row count to dynamic `insertRow()` for valid devices only.                                   |
| Occasionally `show_discovery_table()` raises error or includes invalid entries                | Weak validation of BlueZ object state or mismatch in live objects.    | ✅ Yes         | Added stronger validation with proper exception handling (`DBusException`) during device property access.              |



| **Error Message / Symptom**                                             | **Root Cause**                                                                                                     | **Resolved?** | **Resolution**                                                                                                                                       |
| ----------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| A2DP/OPP profile-specific UI loaded even before the device is connected | UI did not check connection state before showing profile-specific controls (e.g., media streaming, file transfer). | ✅ Yes         | Added device filtering based on valid adapter path and connection status before populating discovery table and enabling profile-related UI elements. |
